---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Sobre Mí | Eugenia Guerrero – Contadora" 
  description="Conoce a Eugenia Guerrero, contadora profesional dedicada a brindar servicios contables accesibles y de calidad para personas y empresas."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-secondary-500 text-white py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold mb-4">
        Sobre Mí
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Conoce mi trayectoria profesional y filosofía de trabajo
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- About Me Content -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="md:w-1/3">
          <!-- Placeholder for professional photo -->
          <div class="bg-secondary-200 h-80 w-full rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shadow-md">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-16 h-16 text-secondary-500">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0zM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0114.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0112 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="md:w-2/3">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-primary-500 mb-6">
            Eugenia Guerrero
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Soy contadora pública con más de 10 años de experiencia en el ámbito contable y fiscal. Mi carrera profesional se ha centrado en ayudar a personas y empresas a gestionar sus obligaciones tributarias y optimizar sus procesos financieros.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Me especializo en brindar servicios contables accesibles y de alta calidad, adaptados a las necesidades específicas de cada cliente. Mi enfoque combina el conocimiento técnico con un servicio personalizado y cercano, asegurando que mis clientes se sientan acompañados en cada paso del proceso.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Mi filosofía de trabajo se basa en la transparencia, la confianza y la continua actualización profesional para ofrecer siempre las mejores soluciones contables.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Mission & Vision -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <div class="rounded-full bg-primary-100 p-3 w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 3v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 006 16.5h2.25M3.75 3h-1.5m1.5 0h16.5m0 0h1.5m-1.5 0v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 0118 16.5h-2.25m-7.5 0h7.5m-7.5 0l-1 3m8.5-3l1 3m0 0l.5 1.5m-.5-1.5h-9.5m0 0l-.5 1.5m.75-9l3-3 2.148 2.148A12.061 12.061 0 0116.5 7.605" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-primary-500 mb-4">Misión</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Democratizar el acceso a servicios contables profesionales, brindando soluciones accesibles, personalizadas y de calidad que permitan a mis clientes enfocarse en su negocio mientras yo me encargo de sus obligaciones contables y fiscales.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <div class="rounded-full bg-primary-100 p-3 w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.036 12.322a1.012 1.012 0 010-.639C3.423 7.51 7.36 4.5 12 4.5c4.638 0 8.573 3.007 9.963 7.178.07.207.07.431 0 .639C20.577 16.49 16.64 19.5 12 19.5c-4.638 0-8.573-3.007-9.963-7.178z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-primary-500 mb-4">Visión</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Ser reconocida como una aliada estratégica para el crecimiento financiero de mis clientes, ofreciendo servicios contables innovadores que combinen la tecnología con un trato humano y cercano, contribuyendo así al éxito y la tranquilidad financiera de las personas y empresas con las que trabajo.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Education & Experience -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-primary-500 mb-8 text-center">
          Formación y Experiencia
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <!-- Experiencia Profesional -->
          <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4 flex items-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6 mr-2 text-primary-500">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M20.25 14.15v4.25c0 1.094-.787 2.036-1.872 2.18-2.087.277-4.216.42-6.378.42s-4.291-.143-6.378-.42c-1.085-.144-1.872-1.086-1.872-2.18v-4.25m16.5 0a2.18 2.18 0 00.75-1.661V8.706c0-1.081-.768-2.015-1.837-2.175a48.114 48.114 0 00-3.413-.387m4.5 8.006c-.194.165-.42.295-.673.38A23.978 23.978 0 0112 15.75c-2.648 0-5.195-.429-7.577-1.22a2.016 2.016 0 01-.673-.38m0 0A2.18 2.18 0 013 12.489V8.706c0-1.081.768-2.015 1.837-2.175a48.111 48.111 0 013.413-.387m7.5 0V5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0013.5 3h-3a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25v.894m7.5 0a48.667 48.667 0 00-7.5 0M12 12.75h.008v.008H12v-.008z" />
              </svg>
              Experiencia Profesional
            </h3>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-3">
                <div class="bg-primary-100 p-2 rounded-lg">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21v-8.25M15.75 21v-8.25M8.25 21v-8.25M3 9l9-6 9 6m-1.5 12V10.332A48.36 48.36 0 0012 9.75c-2.551 0-5.056.2-7.5.582V21M3 21h18M12 6.75h.008v.008H12V6.75z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-600 mb-1">
                    Clínica España
                  </h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                    Gestión contable y tributaria integral para institución de salud
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-3">
                <div class="bg-primary-100 p-2 rounded-lg">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 18.75a60.07 60.07 0 0115.797 2.101c.727.198 1.453-.342 1.453-1.096V18.75M3.75 4.5v.75A.75.75 0 013 6h-.75m0 0v-.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125H20.25M2.25 6v9m18-10.5v.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75h.75m-1.5-1.5h.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v9.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-.375m1.5-1.5H21a.75.75 0 00-.75.75v.75m0 0H3.75m0 0h-.375a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V15m1.5 1.5v-.75A.75.75 0 003 15h-.75M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm3 0h.008v.008H18V10.5zm-12 0h.008v.008H6V10.5z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-600 mb-1">
                    COAC 27 de Abril
                  </h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                    Asesoría contable y auditoría para cooperativa de ahorro y crédito
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-3">
                <div class="bg-primary-100 p-2 rounded-lg">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v12m-3-2.818l.879.659c1.171.879 3.07.879 4.242 0 1.172-.879 1.172-2.303 0-3.182C13.536 12.219 12.768 12 12 12c-.725 0-1.45-.22-2.003-.659-1.106-.879-1.106-2.303 0-3.182s2.9-.879 4.006 0l.415.33M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-600 mb-1">
                    Cooperativa Artesanal del Azuay
                  </h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                    Estados financieros y cumplimiento normativo
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-3">
                <div class="bg-primary-100 p-2 rounded-lg">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 21v-7.5a.75.75 0 01.75-.75h3a.75.75 0 01.75.75V21m-4.5 0H2.36m11.14 0H18m0 0h3.64m-1.39 0V9.349m-16.5 11.65V9.35m0 0a3.001 3.001 0 003.75-.615A2.993 2.993 0 009.75 9.75c.896 0 1.7-.393 2.25-1.016a2.993 2.993 0 002.25 1.016c.896 0 1.7-.393 2.25-1.016a3.001 3.001 0 003.75.614m-16.5 0a3.004 3.004 0 01-.621-4.72L4.318 3.44A1.5 1.5 0 015.378 3h13.243a1.5 1.5 0 011.06.44l1.19 1.189a3 3 0 01-.621 4.72m-13.5 8.65h3.75a.75.75 0 00.75-.75V13.5a.75.75 0 00-.75-.75H6.75a.75.75 0 00-.75.75v3.75c0 .415.336.75.75.75z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-600 mb-1">
                    Importadora Cedillo
                  </h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                    Contabilidad y gestión tributaria para comercio exterior
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-3">
                <div class="bg-primary-100 p-2 rounded-lg">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6.115 5.19l.319 1.913A6 6 0 008.11 10.36L9.75 12l-.387.775c-.217.433-.132.956.21 1.298l1.348 1.348c.21.21.329.497.329.795v1.089c0 .426.24.815.622 1.006l.153.076c.433.217.956.132 1.298-.21l.723-.723a8.7 8.7 0 002.288-4.042 1.087 1.087 0 00-.358-1.099l-1.33-1.108c-.251-.21-.582-.299-.905-.245l-1.17.195a1.125 1.125 0 01-.98-.314l-.295-.295a1.125 1.125 0 010-1.591l.13-.132a1.125 1.125 0 011.3-.21l.603.302a.809.809 0 001.086-1.086L14.25 7.5l1.256-.837a4.5 4.5 0 001.528-1.732l.146-.292M6.115 5.19A9 9 0 1017.18 4.64M6.115 5.19A8.965 8.965 0 0112 3c1.929 0 3.716.607 5.18 1.64" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-600 mb-1">
                    Importadora Ecuador Mundial
                  </h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                    Servicios contables y planificación fiscal
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-3">
                <div class="bg-primary-100 p-2 rounded-lg">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12h3.75M9 15h3.75M9 18h3.75m3 .75H18a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25V6.108c0-1.135-.845-2.098-1.976-2.192a48.424 48.424 0 00-1.123-.08m-5.801 0c-.065.21-.1.433-.1.664 0 .414.336.75.75.75h4.5a.75.75 0 00.75-.75 2.25 2.25 0 00-.1-.664m-5.8 0A2.251 2.251 0 0113.5 2.25H15c1.012 0 1.867.668 2.15 1.586m-5.8 0c-.376.023-.75.05-1.124.08C9.095 4.01 8.25 4.973 8.25 6.108V8.25m0 0H4.875c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h9.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V9.375c0-.621-.504-1.125-1.125-1.125H8.25zM6.75 12h.008v.008H6.75V12zm0 3h.008v.008H6.75V15zm0 3h.008v.008H6.75V18z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-600 mb-1">
                    Audited CIA LTDA
                  </h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                    Auditoría y control interno empresarial
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Formación Académica -->
          <div class="mt-12 border-t border-gray-200 pt-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-6 flex items-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6 mr-2 text-primary-500">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.26 10.147a60.436 60.436 0 00-.491 6.347A48.627 48.627 0 0112 20.904a48.627 48.627 0 018.232-4.41 60.46 60.46 0 00-.491-6.347m-15.482 0a50.57 50.57 0 00-2.658-.813A59.905 59.905 0 0112 3.493a59.902 59.902 0 0110.399 5.84c-.896.248-1.783.52-2.658.814m-15.482 0A50.697 50.697 0 0112 13.489a50.702 50.702 0 017.74-3.342M6.75 15a.75.75 0 100-1.5.75.75 0 000 1.5zm0 0v-3.675A55.378 55.378 0 0112 8.443m-7.007 11.55A5.981 5.981 0 006.75 15.75v-1.5" />
